description:
Arnott’s Cracker Chips Balsamic Vinegar & Sea Salt are perfectly balanced with the tang of balsamic vinegar and a sprinkling of Australian sea salt. Oven-roasted to perfection, it’s a savoury biscuit that delivers a crispy bite you’ll love.

Arnott’s Cracker Chips Balsamic Vinegar & Sea Salt are the perfect cross between a cracker and chip. These crunchy cracker chips are a delicious flavoursome snack for a moment of indulgence. Share a packet of these moreish crackers with friends when you’re enjoying an evening of socialising. Or grab them when you’re looking for an afternoon treat at the park.

• Unique fusion of a cracker and a chip.
• A perfectly balanced of tangy balsamic vinegar and Australian sea salt.
• Oven roasted, never fried.
• No artificial colours or flavours

Oven roasted, never fried'

'Contains no artificial colours or flavours'

Truly Something Else
name: Arnott's Cracker Chips Sea Salt & Balsamic Vinegar 150G
